to_numeric <- function(df) {
    df[,2:6] <- apply(df[,2:6], 2, as.character)
    df[,2:6] <- apply(df[,2:6], 2, as.numeric)
    df
}

SS2 <- to_numeric(SS2)
SZ2 <- to_numeric(SZ2)
HSCE2 <- to_numeric(HSCE2)

POSIXlt_year <- function(df) {
        
    year <- as.POSIXlt(as.character(df[,1]), format = "%Y-%m-%d")$year
    month <- as.POSIXlt(as.character(df[,1]), format = "%Y-%m-%d")$mon+1
    date <- as.POSIXlt(as.character(df[,1]), format = "%Y-%m-%d")
    df$year <- as.character(year)
    df$month <- as.character(month)    
    df$Date <- date
    df
    
}

df_cut <- function(df, year) {
    temp_year = year - 1900
    temp <- df[as.numeric(df$year) >= temp_year,]
    temp
}

SS2 <- POSIXlt_year(SS2)
SZ2 <- POSIXlt_year(SZ2)
HSCE2 <- POSIXlt_year(HSCE2)
HSI2 <- POSIXlt_year(HSI2)

SS2006 <- df_cut(SS2, 2006)
SZ2006 <- df_cut(SZ2, 2006)
HSCE2006 <- df_cut(HSCE2, 2006)
HSI2006 <- df_cut(HSI2, 2006)

HSI2010 <- df_cut(HSI2, 2010)

index.acf <- function(df, col = 'remainder', is.df = TRUE){
  if(is.df) temp <- df[, col]
  else temp <- df

  par(mfrow = c(2,1))
  acf(temp, main = paste('ACF of', col))
  pacf(temp, main = paste('PACF of', col))
  par(mfrow = c(1,1))
}
      
index.acf(HSI2010, col = 'Adj.Close')
In [12]:
HSI.ma <- function(df, col = 'Adj.Close', order = 100){
  temp = df[, col]
  end = length(temp) - 1
  out = rep(0, length(temp))
  out[1] = temp[1]
  for(i in 1:end){
    if(i - order <= 1) j = 1 
    else j = j + 1
    out[i + 1] = sum(temp[j:i])/(i - j + 1)
  }
  out
}
      
HSI.seasons <- function(df, col = 'Adj.Close'){
  df$y = df[, col]
  fit = lm(y ~ 0 + month, data = df)
  predict(fit, newdata = df)
}
      
      
decomp.HSI <- function(df,  col = 'Adj.Close', multiplicative = TRUE, order = 100){
  if(multiplicative) {
    temp = log(df[, col])
    df[, col] = temp
  } else { 
    temp = df[, col] 
  }
  trend = HSI.ma(df, col = col, order = order)
  temp = temp - trend
  df[, col] = temp
  seasonal = HSI.seasons(df, col = col)
  remainder = temp - seasonal
  data.frame(trend = trend, seasonal = seasonal, remainder = remainder)
}
decomp <- decomp.HSI(HSI2010, multiplicative = TRUE, order = 200)

index.stl <- function(df, col = 'diff', span = 0.5, Mult = TRUE){
  if(Mult) {temp <- ts(log(df[, col]), frequency = 246)
  } else {temp <- ts(df[, col], frequency = 246, start = 1)} #STL() requires regular timeseries, we assum there are 246 trading days here
  span = span * length(temp)  
  indexFit <- stl(temp, s.window = "periodic", t.window = span)
  plot(indexFit, main = 'Decompositon of the Index')
  cbind(df, as.data.frame(indexFit$time.series))
}
HSIMult = index.stl(HSI2006, col = 'Adj.Close', span = 0.2)

index.change <- function(df, col = 'Adj.Close', out = 'change'){
  ln <- nrow(df)
  temp <- ts(df[, col], frequency = 246)
  df[2:ln, out] <- diff(temp)
  df <- df[2:ln, ]
  df
}
